{"head":161,"savepointDataFileId":"77232290261","savepointListObject":{},"lastEditTimestamp":1470404533895,"diffChangeset":"Z:1>8g*4*5*6+8f|1=1|1+1$8-5-2016 - Current State of Nebulizer Software - There is an issue with reading battery voltage during RUN state.  I have not looked at it yet - to get something going quickly, I simply disabled the check.  It probably has to do with swapping the ADC reference voltage, but it will be addressed shortly.\n","invalidDiffChangeset":false,"authorList":{"242623211":{"authorName":"Bill Hawkins"}},"diffAuthorList":{"242623211":true},"shouldCreateSavepointBeforeApplyingNextRevision":false,"firstKeyRevision":5,"atext":{"text":"8-5-2016 - Current State of Nebulizer Software - There is an issue with reading battery voltage during RUN state.  I have not looked at it yet - to get something going quickly, I simply disabled the check.  It probably has to do with swapping the ADC reference voltage, but it will be addressed shortly.\n\n","attribs":"*4*5*6+8f|2+2","opCount":2,"appliedAttribsCount":3,"maxAttribsOnSingleOp":3},"pool":{"numToAttrib":{"0":["author","a.4fz9s4pIrvcRKF5l"],"1":["align","left"],"2":["insertorder","first"],"3":["lmkr","1"],"4":["author","242623211"],"5":["font-color-000000","true"],"6":["font-size-medium","true"]},"nextNum":7},"chatHead":-1,"publicStatus":false,"passwordHash":null,"savedRevisions":[]}